{"tid":2138332,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[幫你執屎都要屌]運輸署去信九巴稱未授權巴士總站放椅子供市民午膳","createTime":"2020-08-03T13:45:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-03T14:23:09.000Z","uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8a88c8a1ed3e46674552e8e63fd7f6f3194ab7d8","tid":2138332,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T13:45:16.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】運輸署去信九巴指，如使用巴士總站部分地方作其他用途，需要得到有關部門批准。<br />\n<br />\n九巴日前因應政府的全日禁堂食措施，在午膳時間於三個巴士總站放置多張椅子供市民使用，事後九巴接獲運輸署信件，指九巴事前未有通知署方，便將私人物件放置在政府土地上，有關做法是未獲授權。<br />\n<br />\n運輸署回覆查詢時指，巴士總站屬於政府土地，如營運商想使用巴士總站部分地方作其他用途，需得到有關部門批准，但同意及感謝九巴相關做法。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=400396\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D400396&d=vyHMe5JNZh87BdTcd5o0Ox5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=44832e52\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D400396&h=310f7481\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=400396</a>"},{"pid":"f76623a750426b00ed7a783f6b32b49b1c18c7d6","tid":2138332,"uid":1767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T13:46:45.000Z","msg":"落後政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7236eef8bd2cc05359f93727f25c891b4793f375","tid":2138332,"uid":33939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T13:48:04.000Z","msg":"抵啦，你做得好過政府咪顯得個政府好似好廢咁。"},{"pid":"97feff47db7ac3a4226c1f78f592ac72a96a50bb","tid":2138332,"uid":314604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T13:54:34.000Z","msg":"運輸處已經三番四次咁搞九巴 都係打份工姐 有必要咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdfaf8ba73978517f1d5a09962aef83fa0e03a19","tid":2138332,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"97feff47db7ac3a4226c1f78f592ac72a96a50bb","tid":2138332,"uid":314604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"cit